ry\" is the value with \"Model\" as the label. I'm focusing on \"Agent Factory\" now. I'm considering \"Scale Operations,\" or potentially removing the label for simplicity, or some other generic label. I'm checking to make sure that \"Platform\" doesn't conflict with any rules, since it seems less intrusive.\n\n\n**Finalizing Metric Structure**\n\nI've decided on the final metric structure! I'm now certain about \"Global Delivery Model\", \"Knowledge Graph Factory\" and \"AI Academy\". After a final check, \"Agent Factory Platform\" appears perfect, and I'll keep them as they are, with no need for revision.\n\n\n"}}
